"""
google_agent/planning/teaching_strategy_agent.py
===============================================================================
WORLD-TEACHER TeachingStrategyAgent.

Responsibility:
- Decide HOW to teach a selected node like a world-class human tutor.
- Consume Source/RAG + SelectedPageVision + ConceptExtraction + KnowledgeGraph.
- Produce a clean, source-grounded, board-ready teaching strategy.
- Prepare DetailedExplanationAgent and VisualPlannerAgent.
- Do NOT create final board commands.

Fixes:
- No broad dirty sourceRef repair.
- No empty quote refs.
- No title/unrelated page pollution.
- selectedEvidence / selected page first.
- comparison refs only for comparison steps.
- every teaching step must include clean sourceRefs.
- output includes visualBoardBridge, boardActionPlan, repairRoutes, pacingPlan.

No fixed domain.
No Star Schema hardcoding.
No fake fallback.
===============================================================================
"""

